3 unit Mike’s Hot Honey®
1 unit Demi-Baguette
4 ounce Riocotta

Adjust rack to top position and preheat oven to 425 degrees.

Slice baguette crosswise into 8 rounds. Spread slices out on a baking sheet and drizzle with oil. Toast on top rack of oven until golden brown, 5-10 minutes.

Meanwhile, season ricotta with salt and pepper. Spread ricotta onto toasted baguette slices and top with hot honey. Serve immediately.